metadata.name: Stand Together #1/40
metadata.description:
Stand Together is a dedication piece to the wonderful people I have connected with, laughed with and even sang with since joining the NFT/Twitter space in 2021. I love how we stand together not only in happy times, but in tough times too. 

Just like these rock stacks of the Twelve Apostles standing together while continually getting splashed and smashed by the waves, the NFT space goes through bull and bear markets, yet we stand together & support each other at all times.

Title: Stand Together  
Editions: 40  
Artist: Liyat G Haile  
Dimensions: 4393 x 2934px

Stand Together is the first edition to be released by Liyat G Haile.
